            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@Kumar Harsh, What makes two objects equal is very application specific; not every property of an object should necessarily be taken into consideration, so brute-forcing every property of an object is not a concrete solution either.&lt;/span&gt;

