              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/4441547/aaron-franke&quot; title=&quot;2,548 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Aaron Franke&lt;/a&gt;
